    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。用户完成任务的节点，我是不是标记成'Complete mission'，并且注明是在Education_LMS_Portal里发生的？然后Frontend要调API v1的接口？",
