      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，User到Frontend的消息写'Complete mission (Education_LMS_Portal)'。然后Frontend要POST到API v1的/journeys/{Education_GradeSync}/mint-badge这个端点，GradeSync是我们内部的任务ID。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Frontend",
        "API v1",
        "POST /journeys/{Education_GradeSync}/mint-badge",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上这条线。接下来API v1和Solana devnet的交互是？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Frontend",
        "API v1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "API v1收到请求后，要向Solana devnet发送交易，链上铸造badge。Solana返回signature之后，API v1要把signature和explorerUrl一起回给Frontend。",
      "elements_involved": [
