      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：API到Solana是实线箭头'send transaction'，Solana返回signature用虚线箭头；然后API回Frontend也是虚线，带signature和explorerUrl？",
      "elements_involved": [
