      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。最后Frontend给用户展示成功状态，还要给一个Solscan的链接，让用户能去链上查看。消息写成'Show success + link to Solscan'。",
      "elements_involved": [
